Depends on https://github.com/vuejs/vue/pull/5016

This also adds a default export object so that the following usage will be consistent in both ES and TS:

``` js
import Vue from 'vue'
import Vuex from 'vuex'

Vue.use(Vuex)

const store = new Vuex.Store({
  // ...
})
```
